      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="center" type="letterhead"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.0001.03176_0021-0"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><hi rend="small-caps"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb715">Hotel Kaiserin Elisabeth</rs></hi></hi></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Interurban. Telephon</hi> No. 12</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">Eigentümer: <hi rend="capitals"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb147699">K.</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#kaufmannsund"/><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb147701">H. Seeauer</rs></hi></hi></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print">Telegr.-Adr.:</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><lb/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb715">Elisabethhotel</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb213">Bad Ischl</rs></hi>.</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="small-caps"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb213">Bad Ischl</rs></hi></hi></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Lift<space unit="chars" quantity="10"/>Bäder.</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">= <rs type="place" ref="#pmb429">Salzkammergut</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240">Österreich</rs>. =</hi></seg></seg><dateline><date when="1911-09-10">10. 9. 11</date>.</dateline><salute rend="left">Lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Tief ergriffen von der Nachricht, die ich eben erfahre, habe ich das Bedürfnis, Dir
               teilnehmend die Hand zu drücken u. Dir zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agen, daß ich den <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03476-1"/>Tod Deiner <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb12701">Mutter</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03476-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb12701">Louise Schnitzler</rs> war am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1911-09-09" subtype="date-only"/>
                  verstorben.</note> mit Dir betraure. Das i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t das Schwer<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te, das einen Men<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen
               treffen <del rend="strikethrough">K</del> kann, u. ich wün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che Dir die Kraft, die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en
               Schick<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>als<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlag zu <pb facs="HS.NZ85.0001.03176_0021-1"/>ertragen. Ich werde Deiner
                  <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb12701">Mutter</rs> die Güte u.
               Freund<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chaft, die<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ie mir erwie<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en, nie verge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en. <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann.</signed></p></div>
      </body>
